                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Il est le vrai souverain ; mais",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Quand verra-t-il dans sa marmite",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Un morceau de viande ? Jamais.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour lui le bonheur est un mythe.\nIl est le vrai souverain ; mais\nQuand verra-t-il dans sa marmite\nUn morceau de viande ? Jamais."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Et les petits, dont le ciel aime",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Les doux sourires familiers,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Noir et mystérieux problème !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Vont en loques et sans souliers.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et les petits, dont le ciel aime\nLes doux sourires familiers,\nNoir et mystérieux problème !\nVont en loques et sans souliers."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et, cependant, la forte-en-gueule",
